{"tid":44362,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣孖許晉亨遊日遇初雪勁浪漫","createTime":"2016-12-18T08:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T09:09:06.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a149945ca0e38f80d97b07e55c9496fb6edf4ab6","tid":44362,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"大美人李嘉欣（Michele）出席慈善公益活動，她即席扶助視弱人士步行，並表示是次活動是幫助視弱人士以及推廣環保，因此覺得活動十分有意義，而她自己以往亦曾到尼泊爾參與震災行動。 <br />\n<br />\n身體力行教仔仔幫助人 <br />\n<br />\n問到為何不帶仔仔一同前來參與善舉？她說：「仔仔要返學。（會否帶佢去做探訪？）一路有計劃帶佢去外地探訪，喺香港有做過探訪，解釋畀佢聽幸福唔係必然。（仔仔畫畫咁叻，會否用啲畫做慈善拍賣？）暫時冇咁諗過，佢的確對畫畫有興趣，慈善可以從其他方面入手。咁我哋自己都有個JMJ基金，有參與興建學校行，畀仔仔知道發生緊咩事。」 <br />\n<br />\n結婚周年紀念日講好唔送禮 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於提到聖誕節將至，嘉欣表示屆時會去滑雪，又透露早前與老公許晉亨趁八周年結婚紀念日到了日本旅行。問到老公有否送禮物？她說：「冇咩特別送禮物，我哋講好唔好特登諗嘢送畀大家，計劃咗個旅行，兩個人去，已經好足夠，仲撞正日本第一次隔咗幾十年嚟最早落雪。（初雪好浪漫。）都係㗎！（有冇乘機造人？）唔使等落雪嘅。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/161840_6e8af5e2b11c5755fab6a2a8b216a551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F161840_6e8af5e2b11c5755fab6a2a8b216a551.jpg&h=47eb9643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">李嘉欣同許晉亨去日本難得撞正當地隔幾十年嚟最早落雪，真係幸運喇！</span>"},{"pid":"5eecd7c4ca46be9a2d794d45220672a602359e47","tid":44362,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"大美人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f86cf4c262b7bfe8cf398cb43693abdfe3f2465","tid":44362,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"1042663b8c4c1254bfd2cfeebe5c9a8c872498cb","tid":44362,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我真係恭喜你呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都祝你新婚快樂"},{"pid":"f091141d53fd4291aa903f6826284eca2d707f8b","tid":44362,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/161840_6e8af5e2b11c5755fab6a2a8b216a551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F161840_6e8af5e2b11c5755fab6a2a8b216a551.jpg&h=47eb9643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次見到呢張相就忍唔住笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6f6f5c16837eebfe16c2e45b929a71ede2dc45","tid":44362,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07bdd563fbf3dad1e86a38177ef388bc8493d96e","tid":44362,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea20de722d89d729ccb82c738171776acd11c730","tid":44362,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"好撚嘈啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}